OL,6,FA Second World War bunker in that was
OL,7,Frepurposed amid fears of a nuclear
OL,8,Fattack has opened for a rare public
OL,9,Fvisit.
OL,11,FThe site in the capital St Helier was
OL,12,Fkept a secret for many years after it
OL,13,Fwas designated the island's civil
OL,14,Femergency centre during the Cold War.
OL,16,FThe Government transformed the bunker
OL,17,Fin 1979 in response to the growing
OL,18,Fthreat of global conflict as the
OL,19,FUnited States of America and Russia
OL,20,Fescalated their deep-rooted suspicions
OL,21,Fof each other.
