OL,6,FIt led to a rise in nuclear bombs and
OL,7,Fdefences with bunkers built deep right
OL,8,Facross Europe in the hope that some
OL,9,Fpeople could survive any potential
OL,10,Ffallout, including in Jersey.
OL,12,FTour guide Paul Lister said: "Our role
OL,13,Fhere was to monitor any kind of event
OL,14,Fthat happened and the amount of
OL,15,Fradiation and if necessary, warn the
OL,16,Fpublic over the radio.
