OL,3,CLook inside the secret Cold War bunker
OL,4,Cset up in case of nuclear attack
OL,6,F"If a nuclear event had occurred then
OL,7,Fwe were obliged to come down here and
OL,8,Fdo the job, leaving our family up top
OL,9,Fso we were safe and protected and they
OL,10,Fweren't."
OL,12,FFrom gas masks, radiation suits and
OL,13,FGeiger counters to maps and emergency
OL,14,Fprocedures, the bunker has been frozen
OL,15,Fin time since it was abandoned when
OL,16,Fthe threat diminished.
OL,18,FIt is preserved by the charity Jersey
OL,19,FHeritage and is not regularly open to
OL,20,Fvisitors.
